Many would say they're the same thing.

368
00:13:18,781 --> 00:13:21,656
对  他们都是白痴  创作还是事实
Yes, idiots. Poetry or truth?

369
00:13:22,708 --> 00:13:26,385
我看到过她的脸  是在后来
I saw her face myself. Afterwards.

370
00:13:26,916 --> 00:13:28,031
什么的后来
After what?

371
00:13:28,031 --> 00:13:29,145
你
You?

372
