- I surmised. - What was her name, the bride?

378
00:13:53,947 --> 00:13:56,895
艾米丽娅・瑞克莱蒂  昨天是她的结婚纪念日
Emelia Ricoletti. Yesterday was her wedding anniversary.

379
00:13:56,895 --> 00:13:59,333
