Thomas Ricoletti. Emelia Ricoletti's husband.

385
00:14:31,072 --> 00:14:34,385
大概是在去停尸房辨认遗体的路上吧
Presumably on his way to the morgue to identify her remains?

386
00:14:36,416 --> 00:14:38,885
结果他省了这麻烦
As it turned out, he was saved the trip.

387
00:14:44,927 --> 00:14:49,583
*别忘了我*
*Do not forget me*

388
00:14:49,968 --> 00:14:54,052
*别忘了我*
*Do not forget me*

389
00:14:54,718 --> 00:14:57,843
{\an8}*记住那少女*
*Remember the maid...*

390
00:14:57,322 --> 00:14:58,552
