Why are you doing this? Just tell me who you are!

393
00:15:03,416 --> 00:15:06,343
你听出了我们的歌吗  亲爱的
You recognise our song, my dear?

394
00:15:07,187 --> 00:15:09,427
我在婚礼上唱过
I sang it at our wedding.

395
00:15:14,437 --> 00:15:15,625
艾米丽娅
Emelia?

396
00:15:16,645 --> 00:15:20,260
你死了  你不可能在这里  你死了
You, you're dead, you can't be here, you died!

397
00:15:20,885 --> 00:15:23,114
我美吗  托马斯
Am I not beautiful, Thomas?

398
00:15:23,458 --> 00:15:26,427
跟你娶我那天一样美
As beautiful as the day you married me?

399
00:15:26,812 --> 00:15:28,395
-谁...  -这是怎么回事
- Who... - What the hell is all this about?!

400
00:15:30,583 --> 00:15:34,041
看起来像是什么样  我英俊的朋友
What does it look like, my handsome friend?

401
00:15:36,291 --> 00:15:37,979
这是"枪杆"下的婚姻
It's a shotgun wedding.

402
00:15:47,354 --> 00:15:50,802
不至死亡  永不分离  他们各死了一次
Till death us do part. Twice in this case.

403
00:16:08,687 --> 00:16:09,854
真离奇
Extraordinary.

404
00:16:10,770 --> 00:16:12,229
不可能
Impossible.

405
00:16:12,895 --> 00:16:13,625
太棒了
Superb.

406
00:16:13,625 --> 00:16:15,500
在街头自杀  被尸体谋杀
Suicide as street theatre, murder by corpse.

407
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,739
