- Where are we going? - To the morgue.

410
00:16:19,156 --> 00:16:20,635
一刻也不能耽搁了
There's not a moment to lose,

411
00:16:20,947 --> 00:16:23,322
很少有人会这样说停尸房
which one can so rarely say of a morgue.

412
00:16:23,458 --> 00:16:24,500
那我就坐在这里吗
And am I just to sit here?

413
00:16:24,510 --> 00:16:27,333
当然不是  亲爱的  我们之后会饿的
Not at all, my dear. We'll be hungry later.

414
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:30,052
