他这话什么意思
What's he saying that for?

525
00:22:26,708 --> 00:22:28,281
干你的活儿去
Get back to work!

526
00:22:35,583 --> 00:22:39,604
说吧  福尔摩斯  你肯定有些想法吧
Well, Holmes? Surely you must have some theory?

527
00:22:39,604 --> 00:22:40,854
还没有
Not yet.

528
00:22:41,468 --> 00:22:44,989
此案非常复杂  华生  很棘手
These are deep waters, Watson, deep waters.

529
00:22:47,322 --> 00:22:49,500
