00:23:22,739 --> 00:23:24,395
那多浪费我大脑的记忆空间
that would be an appalling waste of brain space.

541
00:23:24,395 --> 00:23:25,489
我是专攻类型的
I specialise.

542
00:23:25,510 --> 00:23:26,812
这事为什么重要
And what's so important about this?

543
00:23:26,812 --> 00:23:29,062
五起无聊的谋杀案又怎么重要了
What's so important about five boring murders?

544
00:23:29,072 --> 00:23:31,645
这可不无聊  五个男人被害
They're not boring. Five men dead,

545
00:23:31,833 --> 00:23:34,260
死在家中  地上洒满了生米
murdered in their own homes, rice on the floor

546
00:23:34,260 --> 00:23:35,104
就像在婚礼上一样
like at a wedding,

547
00:23:35,104 --> 00:23:38,072
墙上用血着"你"
and the word "You" written in blood on the wall!

548
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:41,916
是她  那个鬼新娘
It's, it's her, it's the Bride.

549
00:23:41,916 --> 00:23:44,020
她又复活了
Somehow she's risen again.

550
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:44,968
解决了
Solved it.

551
00:23:46,062 --> 00:23:47,468
你怎么就破案了
You can't have solved it!

552
00:23:47,468 --> 00:23:49,343
我当然破了  非常简单
Of course I've solved it, it's perfectly simple.

553
00:23:49,343 --> 00:23:51,062
神秘的瑞克莱蒂太太事件
The incident of the mysterious Mrs Ricoletti,

554
00:23:51,062 --> 00:23:52,343
这位来自阴间的凶手
the killer from beyond the grave,

555
00:23:52,343 --> 00:23:54,156
被媒体大肆渲染
has been widely reported in the popular press.

556
00:23:54,156 --> 00:23:56,479
现在有人将自己实施的谋杀
Now people are disguising their own dull little murders

557
00:23:56,479 --> 00:23:57,750
伪装成是鬼魂杀人
as the work of a ghost,

558
00:23:57,750 --> 00:24:00,791
借此迷惑愚蠢的苏格兰场
to confuse the impossibly imbecilic Scotland Yard.

559
00:24:00,791 --> 00:24:02,093
瞧  我破案了
There you are, solved.

560
00:24:02,093 --> 00:24:03,864
你走前跟赫德森太太聊一下
Pay Mrs Hudson a visit on your way out,

561
00:24:03,864 --> 00:24:05,479
她喜欢有参与感
she likes to feel involved.

562
00:24:05,697 --> 00:24:06,635
你确定
You sure?

563
00:24:07,041 --> 00:24:08,343
确定  你走吧
Certainly. Go away.

564
00:24:08,343 --> 00:24:10,250
华生  我准备好了
Watson! I'm ready.

565
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:12,760
戴好帽子穿好鞋  我们有个重要约会
Your hat and boots, we have an important appointment.

566
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:16,708
华生医生几个月前不是搬走了吗
Didn't Dr Watson move out a few months ago?

567
00:24:17,677 --> 00:24:18,958
他确实搬走了  对吧
He did, didn't he?

568
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:21,614
那我一直是在跟谁说话来着
Who have I been talking to all this time?

569
00:24:22,031 --> 00:24:25,239
我代表愚蠢至极的苏格兰场说一句
Well, speaking on behalf of the impossibly imbecilic Scotland Yard,

570
00:24:25,239 --> 00:24:27,031
那张椅子上没人
that chair is definitely empty.

571
00:24:28,333 --> 00:24:29,760
确实没人吧
It is, isn't it?

572
00:24:30,750 --> 00:24:32,510
但我这些日子过得挺不错的
Works surprisingly well, though.

573
00:24:32,614 --> 00:24:34,458
我还以为他有进步了
I actually thought he was improving.

574
00:25:12,687 --> 00:25:13,500
你去哪了
Where have you been?

575
00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:15,375
抱歉  老爷  我今早有些迟了
Sorry, sir, I'm rather behind my time this morning.

576
00:25:15,375 --> 00:25:17,468
你连蛋都不会煮吗
Are you incapable of boiling an egg?!

577
00:25:18,312 --> 00:25:21,041
炉里没有火  到处是灰尘
The fires are rarely lit, there is dust everywhere

578
00:25:21,041 --> 00:25:24,000
你清理我靴子上的泥时差点毁了那双鞋
and you almost destroyed my boots scraping the mud off them.

579
00:25:24,187 --> 00:25:26,312
如果不是我妻子掌管佣人的事
If it wasn't my wife's business to deal with the staff,

580
00:25:26,312 --> 00:25:27,489
我会亲自管教你
I would talk to you myself.

581
00:25:27,489 --> 00:25:28,729
我妻子人呢
Where is my wife?

582
00:25:28,843 --> 00:25:30,760
很抱歉  老爷  夫人出去了
Begging your pardon, sir, but the mistress has gone out.

583
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:32,187
这么早就出门了吗
Out? At this hour of the morning?

584
00:25:32,187 --> 00:25:34,291
是的  老爷  您不知道吗  老爷
Yes, sir. Did you not know that, sir?

585
00:25:34,291 --> 00:25:36,552
她去哪了  她最近总出去
Where did she go? She's always out these days.

586
00:25:36,750 --> 00:25:39,145
跟您正好相反  老爷
Not unlike yourself...sir.

587
00:25:39,395 --> 00:25:40,312
什么
I'm sorry...?

588
00:25:40,854 --> 00:25:42,718
-就是说说我的观察  老爷  -够了
- Just observing, sir. - Well, that's quite enough,

589
00:25:42,718 --> 00:25:43,968
谁让你观察的
nobody asked you to be observant.

590
00:25:43,968 --> 00:25:44,895
抱歉  老爷  我就是说
Sorry, sir, I just meant

591
00:25:44,895 --> 00:25:47,000
你们很少一起待在家里了
you're hardly ever home together any more, sir.

592
00:25:47,458 --> 00:25:49,489
你的言行近乎无礼
You are dangerously close to impertinence.

593
00:25:49,489 --> 00:25:52,062
我要跟我妻子谈下  让她管教下你了
I shall have a word with my wife to have a word with you.

594
00:25:52,916 --> 00:25:56,125
好  老爷  那您什么时候见她呢
Very good, sir. And when will you be seeing her?

595
00:25:57,552 --> 00:25:59,395
-听着...  -我差点忘了  老爷
- Now, listen... - Oh, I nearly forgot, sir.

596
00:25:59,395 --> 00:26:01,614
-有封您的电报  -你忘了
- A telegram came for you. - You forgot?!

597
00:26:01,614 --> 00:26:03,135
没有  只是差点忘了
No, I nearly forgot.

598
00:26:03,135 --> 00:26:04,593
你一上午都在干什么
What have you been doing all morning?

599
00:26:04,593 --> 00:26:06,791
读您《斯特兰德月刊》上的新文章  老爷
Reading your new one in The Strand, sir.

600
00:26:07,718 --> 00:26:08,906
你喜欢吗
Did you enjoy it?

601
00:26:09,208 --> 00:26:10,614
您为什么从不提我  老爷
Why do you never mention me, sir?

602
00:26:10,614 --> 00:26:11,500
下去吧
Go away.

603
00:26:28,531 --> 00:26:31,250
-什么的什么  -黄赤交角
- The what of the what? - The obliquity of the ecliptic.

604
00:26:31,364 --> 00:26:33,729
你说"速来"  我以为是很重要的事
"Come at once," You said. I assumed it was important.

605
00:26:33,729 --> 00:26:36,406
是很重要  那是地球的赤道面
It is. It's the inclination of the earth's equator

606
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,854
与其绕太阳运行的轨道平面的夹角
to the path of the sun on the celestial plane.

607
00:26:39,854 --> 00:26:40,677
你是刚学的吧
You been swotting up?

608
00:26:40,677 --> 00:26:42,083
-我为什么要这么做  -为了显得聪明
- Why would I do that? - To sound clever.

609
00:26:42,093 --> 00:26:44,395
-我本就聪明  -我懂了
- I am clever. - Oh, oh, I see.

610
00:26:44,656 --> 00:26:45,729
懂什么了
You see what?

611
00:26:46,114 --> 00:26:50,322
我推理我们是要去见某个比你聪明的人
I deduce we're on our way to see someone cleverer than you.

612
00:26:51,708 --> 00:26:52,708
闭嘴
Shut up.

613
00:28:06,468 --> 00:28:07,479
什么
Sorry, what?

614
00:28:26,552 --> 00:28:30,677
对想研究人类的人来说  这里最合适
To anyone who wishes to study mankind, this is the spot.

615
00:28:30,677 --> 00:28:32,645
也很方便  毕竟你那不断扩张的屁股
Handy really, as your ever-expanding backside

616
00:28:32,645 --> 00:28:33,937
永远粘在了这里
is permanently glued to it.

617
00:28:33,937 --> 00:28:34,947
早上好  我的哥哥
Good morning, brother mine.

618
00:28:34,947 --> 00:28:37,270
夏洛克  华生医生
Sherlock. Dr Watson.

619
00:28:38,437 --> 00:28:40,135
您看上去  很不错  先生
You look...well, sir.

620
00:28:40,135 --> 00:28:42,729
真的吗  我觉得我看上去很巨大
Really? I rather thought I looked enormous.

621
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:45,687
既然您提到了  这种程度的暴饮暴食
Well, now you mention it, this level of consumption

622
00:28:45,687 --> 00:28:49,322
对您的健康危害极大
is incredibly injurious to your health.

623
00:28:49,333 --> 00:28:51,281
-您的心脏  -不用担心那个  华生
- Your heart... - No need to worry on that score, Watson.

624
00:28:51,281 --> 00:28:54,531
-不吗  -那个器官只会待在一个宽敞的地方
- No? - There's only a large cavity where that organ should reside.

625
00:28:54,531 --> 00:28:57,489
-家族通病  -我不是故意说话尖刻
- It's a family trait. - Oh, I wasn't being critical.

626
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:58,770
如果您继续这样  先生
If you continue like this, sir,

627
00:28:58,770 --> 00:29:01,020
我觉得您最多能活五年
I give you five years at the most.

628
00:29:01,031 --> 00:29:03,208
五年  我们觉得也就是三年
Five? We thought three,

629
00:29:03,208 --> 00:29:04,218
对吧  夏洛克
did we not, Sherlock?

630
00:29:04,218 --> 00:29:05,406
我还是倾向于四年
I'm still inclined to four.

631
00:29:05,406 --> 00:29:08,208
还是这样  你看到了却不懂观察
As ever, you see but you do not observe.

632
00:29:08,208 --> 00:29:10,135
注意我眼白的颜色发生了变化
Note the discolouration in the whites of my eyes,

633
00:29:10,145 --> 00:29:12,541
角膜周围出现可见的脂肪圈
the visible rings of fat around the corneas.

634
00:29:12,541 --> 00:29:13,854
你是对的  我改赌三年
Yes, you're right. I'm changing my bet to three years,

635
00:29:13,854 --> 00:29:15,510
-四个月零十一天  -打赌
- four months and 11 days. - A bet?!

636
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:17,229
我理解你不赞同  华生
I understand your disapproval, Watson,

637
00:29:17,343 --> 00:29:18,510
但他好胜心强
but if he's feeling competitive,

638
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:20,645
可以自己控制早点死亡
it's perfectly within his power to die early.

639
00:29:20,645 --> 00:29:22,437
这也是要冒的风险
That's a risk you'll have to take.

640
00:29:22,895 --> 00:29:24,260
你在拿自己的性命打赌
You're gambling with your own life?

641
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:27,406
为什么不  比拿别人的命打赌有意思多了
Why not? It's so much more exciting than gambling with others'.

642
00:29:27,406 --> 00:29:29,416
整三年  如果你吃了那个葡萄干布丁的话
Three years flat - if you eat that plum pudding!

643
00:29:29,416 --> 00:29:29,989
就这么定了
Done.

644
00:29:36,635 --> 00:29:40,333
我以为几天前会因为领主庄园的案子见到你呢
I expected to see you a few days ago about the Manor House case.

645
00:29:40,333 --> 00:29:42,427
我觉得那案子你会有点力不从心
I thought you might be a little out of your depth there.

646
00:29:42,427 --> 00:29:43,906
没有  我解决了
No. I solved it.

647
00:29:43,906 --> 00:29:46,500
-肯定是亚当斯  -是亚当斯
- It was Adams, of course. - Yes, it was Adams.

648
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:48,062
嫉妒杀人
Murderous jealousy.

649
00:29:48,062 --> 00:29:50,645
他给皇家天文学会写了一篇
He'd written a paper for the Royal Astronomical Society

650
00:29:50,645 --> 00:29:52,906
关于黄赤交角的论文
on the obliquity of the ecliptic,

651
00:29:52,906 --> 00:29:54,052
然后又读到另一篇
and then read another

652
00:29:54,052 --> 00:29:55,718
比他写的好的
that seemed to surpass it.

653
00:29:55,718 --> 00:29:56,718
我知道  我读了
I know, I read it.

654
00:29:56,718 --> 00:29:58,052
你看明白了吗
Did you understand it?

655
00:29:58,104 --> 00:30:00,520
我当然明白了  很浅显易懂
Yes, of course I understood it, it was perfectly simple.

656
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:03,020
不是  你明白嫉妒杀人吗
No, did you understand the murderous jealousy?

657
00:30:03,166 --> 00:30:04,375
一个伟大的大脑
It is no easy thing

658
00:30:04,385 --> 00:30:07,718
去考虑一个更伟大的大脑可不容易
for a great mind to contemplate a still greater one.

659
00:30:09,333 --> 00:30:11,760
你召我来就是为了羞辱我吗
Did you summon me here just to humiliate me?

660
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,937
是的
Yes.

661
00:30:12,937 --> 00:30:15,645
当然不是  但这是最大的乐趣
Of course not, but it is by far the greater pleasure.

662
00:30:15,645 --> 00:30:17,291
那你能不能解释下为什么要召
Then would you mind explaining exactly why you did summon...?

663
00:30:17,291 --> 00:30:20,604
我们的生活方式受到了一个无形敌人的威胁
Our way of life is under threat from an invisible enemy.

664
00:30:20,927 --> 00:30:23,843
他们每天都常伴我们身边
One that hovers at our elbow on a daily basis.

665
00:30:24,145 --> 00:30:25,895
这些敌人无处不在
These enemies are everywhere...

666
00:30:26,625 --> 00:30:27,885
无人发现
undetected...

667
00:30:28,875 --> 00:30:30,614
无法阻止
and unstoppable.

668
00:30:30,791 --> 00:30:32,031
社会主义者
Socialists?

669
00:30:32,416 --> 00:30:34,666
不是社会主义者  医生  不是
Not socialists, Doctor, no.

670
00:30:34,666 --> 00:30:35,989
-无政府主义者  -不是
- Anarchists? - No.

671
00:30:35,989 --> 00:30:38,458
法国人  妇女参政权论者
The French? The suffragists?

672
00:30:38,770 --> 00:30:41,375
还有什么大规模团体是你不担心的吗
Is there any large body of people you're not concerned about?

673
00:30:41,375 --> 00:30:44,458
华生医生永远心怀警惕  详说
Dr Watson is endlessly vigilant. Elaborate...

674
00:30:44,458 --> 00:30:45,854
不  去调查
No. Investigate.

675
00:30:45,854 --> 00:30:48,604
这是我的推测  我需要你去证实
This is a conjecture of mine, I need you to confirm it.

676
00:30:48,604 --> 00:30:50,250
我给你个案子
I'm sending you a case.

677
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:52,343
-苏格兰人  -苏格兰人
- The Scots? - The Scots?!

678
00:30:52,614 --> 00:30:54,447
你是否知道最近
Are you aware of recent theories concerning

679
00:30:54,458 --> 00:30:55,937
关于妄想症的理论
what is known as paranoia?

680
00:30:55,937 --> 00:30:57,625
听着像是塞尔维亚人
Oh, sounds Serbian.

681
00:30:57,927 --> 00:31:00,666
会有个女人去找你  卡迈克夫人
A woman will call on you. Lady Carmichael.

682
00:31:00,666 --> 00:31:02,093
你得接她的案子
I want you to take her case.

683
00:31:02,104 --> 00:31:04,083
但这些敌人  如果你不告诉我们
But these enemies, how are we to defeat them

684
00:31:04,083 --> 00:31:05,510
我们怎么打败他们
if you won't tell us about them?

685
00:31:05,625 --> 00:31:07,427
我们不会打败他们
We don't defeat them.

686
00:31:07,427 --> 00:31:09,583
我们几乎绝对要输给他们
We most certainly lose to them.

687
00:31:10,104 --> 00:31:11,125
为什么
Why?

688
00:31:13,333 --> 00:31:16,833
因为他们是正确的  我们是错的
Because they are right. And we are wrong.

689
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,989
卡迈克夫人的案子  是什么
Lady Carmichael's case, what is it?

690
00:31:19,989 --> 00:31:22,625
放心  会有值得你注意的地方
Rest assured, it has features of interest.

691
00:31:22,625 --> 00:31:24,968
-我从没这么说过  -你真说过
- I never really say that. - You really do.

692
00:31:25,218 --> 00:31:26,625
我估计你已经解决了
And you've solved it already, I assume?

693
00:31:26,625 --> 00:31:30,916
只是设想而已  我要你去跑腿
Only in my head. I need you for the, er, legwork.

694
00:31:30,916 --> 00:31:32,770
为什么不告诉我们你的答案
Why not just tell us your solution?

695
00:31:32,781 --> 00:31:34,687
那还有什么意思呢
And where would be the sport in that?

696
00:31:35,125 --> 00:31:36,218
你愿意接吗  夏洛克
Will you do it, Sherlock?

697
00:31:36,218 --> 00:31:38,906
这绝对是极好的消遣
I can promise you a superior distraction.

698
00:31:39,125 --> 00:31:41,479
我有一个条件  你再吃一个葡萄干布丁
On one condition. Have another plum pudding.

699
00:31:41,479 --> 00:31:42,812
本来就准备吃了
There's one on the way.

700
00:31:42,812 --> 00:31:44,500
两年十一个月四天
Two years, 11 months and four days.

701
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:49,145
开始好玩喽  滴答  滴答  滴答
Ha, it's getting exciting now! Ticktock, ticktock, ticktock.

702
00:31:52,822 --> 00:31:54,885
谢谢  怀尔德
Thank you, Wilder.

703
00:31:54,885 --> 00:31:57,979
有一位梅尔斯先生要见你  福尔摩斯先生
Also, a Mr Melas to see you, Mr Holmes.

704
00:31:57,979 --> 00:32:01,322
